name: Throbbing Graffiti Trench Foot
description:
This is an ode to the common ailment that adventurers attempt to prevent but become afflicted with nonetheless. I am speaking to you, the boundary-pushing explorer who thrives off-trail with map and compass in hand navigating the wild backcountry.  The driven ultra runner who prefers tackling marathon distances day after day or the adventure racer who happily alternates between clip-less biking footwear, aggressively lugged trail shoes, and double-winged paddles for days and miles on end.  I hope this image can find its way into your collection because you truly understand the effort required to acquire feet like these.    

Dimensions: 1665 x 2500 pixels
